  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CARDBOARD WALK!</h2>A relaxed platformer to hop around while collecting the lost CDs of Connie, a well-known DJ. Help the bunny to recover them while exploring cardboard and paper environments.<br><br>No need to hurry though, take your time and enjoy the island as you prefear!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/eb3e35ad82ed10aac6ab2c522c9c2701.poster.avif?t=1718677112\" width=574 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/eb3e35ad82ed10aac6ab2c522c9c2701.webm?t=1718677112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/eb3e35ad82ed10aac6ab2c522c9c2701.mp4?t=1718677112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore areas like Paint Hills, Cutout Forest or Paper Bay, among others!</li><li>Unlock skins for the bun with your progress!</li><li>40 CDs to collect with unique illustrations!</li><li>Several Sub-Areas with minigames and platforming challenges!</li><li>Cute Bunns!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/a545f9b609c15abd13826739a8f795a6.poster.avif?t=1718677112\" width=574 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/a545f9b609c15abd13826739a8f795a6.webm?t=1718677112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2004590/extras/a545f9b609c15abd13826739a8f795a6.mp4?t=1718677112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUN BUN CONBUNN!</h2>Connie is a well-known DJ in Cardbun Island. Her artistic name is Conbunn! Her friend Cell is a bird, and she has lost the \"Conbunn Discs\" (CDs) that Connie needed before a concert. Collect a good amount of them and reach the top to perform that night session!",
